## 🚀 Feature Proposal

Create async iterable for CSV file just it exists for xlsx - ExcelJS.stream.xlsx.WorkbookReader

## Motivation

I am trying to read a huge csv files using streaming. While the documents does have
```js
const workbookReader = new ExcelJS.stream.xlsx.WorkbookReader('./file.xlsx');
for await (const worksheetReader of workbookReader) {
  for await (const row of worksheetReader) {
    // ...
  }
}
```

I am not able to use this with csv files.

## Example
It would be great if we use something like this csv files
```js
const csvSheetReader = new ExcelJS.stream.csv.WorkbookReader('./file.csv');
for await (const row of csvSheetReader) {
    // ...
}

```
